{"data":[{"date":"15:21 22/08","title":"Manchester \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t Arsenal-Wenger th\u1ee9 hai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/manchester-dang-tro-thanh-mot-arsenalwenger-thu-hai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ian Wright bi quan nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111ang d\u1ea7n sa l\u1ea7y v\u00e0o c\u01a1n kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng l\u1ed1i tho\u00e1t nh\u01b0 Arsenal nh\u1eefng n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Arsene Wenger.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Manchester United d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jose Mourinho, c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i, d\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0nh v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015-16 c\u1ee7a Chelsea khi \u00f4ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Gi\u00e1ng Sinh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Arsenal th\u1eddi Wenger h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Arsenal th\u1eddi Wenger h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/man-utd-gio-chang-khac-nao-tro-he-cho-thien-ha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ian Wright th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal nh\u1eefng n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i t\u00e0n d\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Arsene Wenger. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i: \u201c\u0110\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Man Utd hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee9u ch\u1eefa v\u1edbi Mourinho r\u1ed3i, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p t\u00f4i c\u00f3 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0o.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee9ng n\u0103m th\u1ee9 ba c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u00e0 nghe c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ra m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn r\u1ed3i. Theo nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c nhau, Man Utd giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y \u0111ang bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t Arsenal th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 cu\u1ed1i tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Arsene Wenger, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00f4 v\u1ecdng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Mourinho \u0111ang m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn s\u00e2u s\u1eafc v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o va c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Tottenham s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00e0n ly.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-cay-dang-chia-se-ve-tran-thua-tham-o-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194853.html\">Man Utd thua th\u1ea3m: \u0110\u00fang r\u1ed3i Jose, ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p!</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton cho th\u1ea5y Jose Mourinho gi\u1edd \u1edf v\u1ecb th\u1ebf m\u00e0 l\u1eddi m\u1ec9a mai Man City nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Pep Guardiola ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p n\u1eefa r\u1ed3i,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194855.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/Du-am-Brighton-vs-MU-Dung-roi-Jose,-tien-khong-the-mua-dang-cap-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-vs-man-city-172-194855.html\">M.U phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Jose Mourinho: Con thuy\u1ec1n m\u1ea5t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01b0\u1edbng</span><br>\r\nN\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u00e1y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn b\u1ecb k\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton. L\u1eddi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2655","checkdouble":"195074"},{"date":"15:22 22/08","title":"Tay \u0111ua Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/tay-dua-nguyen-thi-that-that-bai-o-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh HC v\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng V\u0110V qu\u00ea An Giang ch\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua 104 km t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u01b0a 22/8, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1eddng 104 km c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u1eef \u1edf Asiad 2018. Tay \u0111ua qu\u00ea An Giang li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong nh\u00f3m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u khi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u00f4i v\u1ec1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ee9t l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng. Chung cu\u1ed9c, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 5 v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 2 gi\u1edd 57 ph\u00fat 35 gi\u00e2y.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tay \u0111ua Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tay \u0111ua Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/that1-6618-1534925342.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u01b0a 22/8. \u1ea2nh: \u0110\u1ee9c \u0110\u1ed3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0nh HC v\u00e0ng l\u00e0 V\u0110V c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c Na Ahreum v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch 2 gi\u1edd 55 ph\u00fat 47 gi\u00e2y (nhanh h\u01a1n Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt 1 ph\u00fat 48 gi\u00e2y). Tay \u0111ua ng\u01b0\u1eddi Trung Qu\u1ed1c Pu Yixian \u0111o\u1ea1t HC b\u1ea1c c\u00f2n HC \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 cua r\u01a1 Yonamine Eri c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua di\u1ec5n ra, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u 22/8. H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 2 v\u1eeba qua, c\u00f4 t\u1eebng \u0111o\u1ea1t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111ua xe \u0111\u1ea1p ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Myanmar khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh l\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh 106 km sau trong 3 gi\u1edd 11 ph\u00fat 59 gi\u00e2y. C\u00f2n \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Asiad, tay \u0111ua ng\u01b0\u1eddi An Giang t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh HC b\u1ea1c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tay \u0111ua c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u00f4i t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f4 \u1ea5y cao h\u01a1n t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t b\u1eadc. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u00e0o c\u1ea3. Xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u00f4i\", Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt chia s\u1ebb sau khi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede n\u1ed9i dung n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb Thi c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 11, ch\u1eadm h\u01a1n V\u0110V gi\u00e0nh HC v\u00e0ng Na Ahreum 2 ph\u00fat 53 gi\u00e2y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTheo ngoisao.net<br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2654","checkdouble":"195075"},{"date":"16:06 22/08","title":"Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng HLV Klopp v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1eeb Naby Keita","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/khoi-dau-an-tuong-hlv-klopp-van-doi-hoi-nhieu-hon-tu-naby-keita.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng West Ham gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB c\u0169 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sai khi \u0111\u1ea9y anh ra \u0111i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wilshere ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Arsenal quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Jack Wilshere. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi m\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 v\u00e0 anh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua, Wilshere li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Anh ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng theo \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/wilshere-phat-bieu-ve-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd sai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Arsene Wenger, Wilshere t\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Mikel Arteta s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Unai Emery m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 Wilshere ra \u0111i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi West Ham.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng minh Arsenal sai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 11 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal, Jack Wilshere chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u CLB c\u0169 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y tr\u00ean ch\u00ednh s\u00e2n Emirates t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 3 Premier League. Nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp n\u00e0y, Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 x\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sai khi h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cArsenal \u0111\u00e3 sai khi ru\u1ed3ng b\u1ecf t\u00f4i. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y\u201d, Wilshere n\u00f3i. \u201cS\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn Emirates v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Bolton hay Bournemouth.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWest Ham \u0111ang kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 khi thua l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bournemouth. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Wilshere t\u1ef1 tin h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i cho Arsenal, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Emery.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i mong ch\u1edd\u201d, Wilshere n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a West Ham.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/manchester-dang-tro-thanh-mot-arsenalwenger-thu-hai-172-195074.html\">Manchester \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t Arsenal-Wenger th\u1ee9 hai</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/neville-arsenal-khong-dang-nhan-nhung-chi-trich-172-195070.html\">Neville: Arsenal kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-khong-ngai-tram-cong-than-arsenal-172-195069.html\">Emery kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i tr\u1ea3m c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-yeu-cau-arsenal-tuc-toc-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-ramsey-172-195042.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i gi\u1ee5c Arsenal t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-van-chua-the-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-ramsey-vi-172-195040.html\">Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey v\u00ec...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-dang-phai-chien-dau-cho-tuong-lai-o-arsenal-172-195031.html\">Ozil \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2653","checkdouble":"195077"},{"date":"16:30 22/08","title":"Chelsea c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid v\u1ee5 Marcos Alonso","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/chelsea-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-2-doi-bong-thanh-madrid-vu-marcos-alonso.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ea1i gia La Liga quan t\u00e2m Alonso</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Alonso ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf La Liga mu\u1ed1n Chelsea b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf La Liga mu\u1ed1n Chelsea b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/chelsea-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-2-doi-bong-thanh-madrid-vu-marcos-alonso.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcos Alonso ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/marcos-alonso-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-180-182943.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Marcos Alonso</span>, Atletico Madrid v\u00e0 Barca c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf La Liga ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u1eb1m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf La Liga hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Tuy nhi\u00ean Chelsea \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea khong ban Marcos Alonso\" title=\"Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/chelsea-khong-ban-marcos-alonso.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Marcos Alonso \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ra \u0111i. Chelsea s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho Alonso.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Huddersfield 3-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 Arsenal 3-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u1ede hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y Alonso \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i mang v\u1ec1 1 qu\u1ea3 11m, \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2652","checkdouble":"195078"},{"date":"16:14 22/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c Jorginho sau kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u trong m\u01a1 \u1edf Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/nguoi-dai-dien-tang-boc-jorginho-sau-khoi-dau-trong-mo-o-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Jorginho t\u1ea1i Chelsea kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean b\u1edfi \u201cc\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u\u201d.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp kh\u00e1 nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri c\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Chelsea. V\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Joao Santos kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd nghi ng\u1edd v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/nguoi-dai-dien-tang-boc-jorginho-sau-khoi-dau-trong-mo-cung-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Chelsea r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 n\u00f3i ti\u1ebfng Anh r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y Jorginho kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Chelsea c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t th\u00ec c\u1eadu ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Chelsea kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 v\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Blues l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal trong tr\u1eadn derby London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;Jorginho r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Arsenal. C\u00f3 t\u1edbi 50 C\u0110V t\u1eeb Napoli \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 xin ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh sau tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao ch\u00fang t\u00f4i y\u00eau Naples v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef t\u00ecnh y\u00eau n\u00e0y. S\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00f9 Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi London&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-2-doi-bong-thanh-madrid-vu-marcos-alonso-172-195078.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid v\u1ee5 Marcos Alonso</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lucas-piazon-sap-roi-chelsea-172-195071.html\">&ldquo;H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i&rdquo; Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb sang Ligue 1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2651","checkdouble":"195082"},{"date":"17:20 22/08","title":"Wilshere: \u201cArsenal \u0111\u00e3 sai khi ru\u1ed3ng b\u1ecf t\u00f4i\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/wilshere-phat-bieu-ve-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng West Ham gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB c\u0169 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sai khi \u0111\u1ea9y anh ra \u0111i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wilshere ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Arsenal quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Jack Wilshere. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi m\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 v\u00e0 anh bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua, Wilshere li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Anh ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng theo \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/wilshere-phat-bieu-ve-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd sai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Arsene Wenger, Wilshere t\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Mikel Arteta s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Unai Emery m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 Wilshere ra \u0111i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau, anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi West Ham.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng minh Arsenal sai</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 11 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal, Jack Wilshere chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u CLB c\u0169 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y tr\u00ean ch\u00ednh s\u00e2n Emirates t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 3 Premier League. Nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp n\u00e0y, Jack Wilshere ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 x\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 sai khi h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cArsenal \u0111\u00e3 sai khi ru\u1ed3ng b\u1ecf t\u00f4i. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y\u201d, Wilshere n\u00f3i. \u201cS\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn Emirates v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Bolton hay Bournemouth.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nWest Ham \u0111ang kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 khi thua l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Liverpool v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bournemouth. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Wilshere t\u1ef1 tin h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i cho Arsenal, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Emery.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i mong ch\u1edd\u201d, Wilshere n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a West Ham.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/manchester-dang-tro-thanh-mot-arsenalwenger-thu-hai-172-195074.html\">Manchester \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t Arsenal-Wenger th\u1ee9 hai</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/neville-arsenal-khong-dang-nhan-nhung-chi-trich-172-195070.html\">Neville: Arsenal kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-khong-ngai-tram-cong-than-arsenal-172-195069.html\">Emery kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i tr\u1ea3m c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-yeu-cau-arsenal-tuc-toc-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-ramsey-172-195042.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i gi\u1ee5c Arsenal t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-van-chua-the-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-ramsey-vi-172-195040.html\">Arsenal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey v\u00ec...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ozil-dang-phai-chien-dau-cho-tuong-lai-o-arsenal-172-195031.html\">Ozil \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Arsenal</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2650","checkdouble":"195084"},{"date":"17:49 22/08","title":"Lewandowski gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Bayern","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/robert-lewandowski-phat-bieu-ve-bayern-munich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Robert Lewandowski ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich. Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai t\u1ea1i CLB, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9ng ra b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lewandowski kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Bayern</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRobert Lewandowski chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Bayern Munich t\u1eeb Dortmund m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2014. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan lu\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 155 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 197 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng cho Bayern.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19, Lewandowski c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n sau 2 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Eintracht Frankfurt t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Drochtersen t\u1ea1i c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Robert Lewandowski ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Robert Lewandowski ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/robert-lewandowski-phat-bieu-ve-bayern-munich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Robert Lewandowski ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Lewandowski mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bayern m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c. \u201cV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4, th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u00f4i\u201d, Robert Lewandowski ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich tr\u00ean Sport Bild.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed9c khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o t\u1eeb ph\u00eda CLB. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o trong 2, 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9t nhi\u00ean m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1ed5i l\u1eeda thi\u00eau ch\u00e1y t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00f4i v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1ea3 c\u00e1c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee9ng ra b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vui v\u1ebb \u1edf Munich trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u1ebfn gi\u1edd, n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ngu\u00f4i ngoai ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Bayern Munich tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/bayern-munich-nhan-tin-cuc-vui-tu-tru-cot-193-194414.html\">Bayern Munich nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c vui t\u1eeb tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/thomas-muller-phat-bieu-ve-robert-lewandowski-193-194398.html\">T\u1ea1i sao Bayern kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski cho Real v\u00e0 M.U?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-frankfurt-05-bayern-munich-sieu-cup-duc-2018-330-194360.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Frankfurt 0-5 Bayern Munich (Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-dam-phan-chieu-mo-boateng-197-194077.html\">PSG \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-jerome-boateng-khong-phai-lua-chon-hoan-hao-voi-mu-172-194042.html\">V\u00ec sao Jerome Boateng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi MU?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2649","checkdouble":"195085"},{"date":"17:47 22/08","title":"\"Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/viet-nam-can-tan-cong-phu-dau-truoc-bahrain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ASIAD 2018, BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 g\u1ee3i \u00fd v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i c\u1ea5p ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Bahrain, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c, BLV V\u0169 Quang Huy \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quang Huy cho bi\u1ebft, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Bahrain b\u1edfi h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 11 b\u1eadc tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng. V\u00e0 cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 nh\u01b0 Saudi Arabia, Iraq hay UAE, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1eeda tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, trong khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Nh\u00ecn m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb&rdquo; &ndash; BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Zing.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-du-doan-thanh-tich-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-tai-AS-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;V\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1eeda tr\u00ean, ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ngay t\u1eeb khi nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i e ng\u1ea1i Bahrain. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, BLV Quang Huy chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia tay gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc khi H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. Vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-hinh-olympic-viet-nam-dau-bahrain-su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot-168-195087.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/doi-hinh-olympic-viet-nam-dau-bahrain-su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-hinh-olympic-viet-nam-dau-bahrain-su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot-168-195087.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u Bahrain: S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1edfi ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Park Hang...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-tiep-tuc-dua-hlv-park-hang-seo-len-may-xanh-168-195073.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/bao-han-tiep-tuc-dua-hlv-park-hang-seo-len-may-xanh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-tiep-tuc-dua-hlv-park-hang-seo-len-may-xanh-168-195073.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00ean m\u00e2y xanh</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Kim chi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195054.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195054.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Bahrain: K\u1ebb th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Bahrain ch\u1ec9 mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U21 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2648","checkdouble":"195086"},{"date":"17:25 22/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea5u Bahrain: S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/doi-hinh-olympic-viet-nam-dau-bahrain-su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1edfi ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out ASIAD 2018, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mong mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng ri\u00eang g\u00ec v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Bahrain t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m b\u1edfi ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eaft.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u l\u1ea1c quan l\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n n\u00e0o su\u1ed1t 270 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 1 trong 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ASIAD.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Doi-hinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Bahrain-Su-tro-lai-cua-cac-tru-cot-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 3 trung v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang 'bay cao' \u1edf ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 3 trung v\u1ec7 Duy M\u1ea1nh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0103n \u00fd v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 3 n\u00e0y \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u00e0ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nh\u00e0n nh\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal, khi m\u00e0 tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng \u00edt khi xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea3 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Duy M\u1ea1nh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Bahrain v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn V\u0103n Thanh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Quang H\u1ea3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Song ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 \u00f4ng Park mang t\u1edbi ASIAD 2018?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>B\u00e0i to\u00e0n \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain, b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c hay trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eefu D\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i tranh ch\u1ea5p, anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m l\u00e1 ch\u1eafn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u1eeb xa tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i nguy h\u1ea1i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e8 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ee5 Ph\u1ea1m \u0110\u1ee9c Huy - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3ng vai d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Duc Huy va Xuan Truong da cap tai U23 Viet Nam\" title=\"\u0110\u1ee9c Huy v\u00e0 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-Ai-se-sat-canh-cung-tien-ve-Xuan-Truong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ee9c Huy s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c, kinh nghi\u1ec7m hay kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p th\u00ec \u0110\u1ee9c Huy c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4, tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n \u0110\u1ee9c Huy \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quang H\u1ea3i hay Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n t\u1ed1t. V\u00e0 v\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh thay ph\u1ea7n H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Sau hai tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 99% Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a HAGL thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c m\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 &quot;c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh&quot; c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo cho v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien ve Xuan Truong\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo &quot;c\u1ea5t k\u1ef9&quot; cho v\u00f2ng 1/8</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Bahrain. T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng HAGL, v\u00e0 khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, anh ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 t\u1ed1i mai 23/8. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ASIAD. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi tham d\u1ef1 c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 \u00e1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/Doi-hinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-tiep-tuc-dua-hlv-park-hang-seo-len-may-xanh-168-195073.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/bao-han-tiep-tuc-dua-hlv-park-hang-seo-len-may-xanh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-tiep-tuc-dua-hlv-park-hang-seo-len-may-xanh-168-195073.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00ean m\u00e2y xanh</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Kim chi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh cho nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-168-195059.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-noi-gi-ve-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-168-195059.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia n\u1ed9i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i mai, c\u00e1c v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 trong n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195054.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-truong-olympic-bahrain-ke-thach-thuc-giac-mo-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-195054.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Bahrain: K\u1ebb th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Bahrain ch\u1ec9 mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U21 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2647","checkdouble":"195087"},{"date":"17:24 22/08","title":"NGolo Kante to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/22/ngolo-kante-toan-dien-nhu-the-nao-duoi-thoi-hlv-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>NGolo Kante t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Maurizio Sarri, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kante to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-3 ho\u1eb7c 3-5-2 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Antonio Conte \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay b\u1eb1ng 4-3-3. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua nh\u01b0 David Luiz, Ross Barkley hay Pedro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"NGolo Kante t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong v\u00e0i tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"NGolo Kante t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong v\u00e0i tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/NGolo-Kante-toa-sang-ruc-ro-trong-vai-tro-moi-duoi-thoi-HLV-Sarri-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt khi khai th\u00e1c NGolo Kante trong vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y hay d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Antonio Conte c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri, Kante kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed &ldquo;m\u1ecf neo&rdquo;. C\u1ef1u HLV Napoli \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e2n binh Jorginho trong vai tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Jorginho ch\u01a1i g\u1ea7n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t, Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n. HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 tham gia nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u1ef1u sao Leicester \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kante to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 Kante \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante choi toan dien truoc Arsenal\" title=\"Kante ch\u01a1i to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/kante-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante ch\u01a1i to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Kante d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1edbi 3 l\u1ea7n, g\u1ea5p 4 l\u1ea7n m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 4 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Kante ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng 0.5 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal anh c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Kante th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, anh c\u0169ng ch\u0103m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa h\u01a1n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield, Kante l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Chelsea nh\u1edd m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n tung ra nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League, Kante ch\u1ec9 ghi 3 b\u00e0n, m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u00f9 ra s\u00e2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 cho th\u1ea5y anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Kante c\u00f2n tham gia r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 70 l\u1ea7n, tung ra 62 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 92%.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante dang choi cuc tot trong vai tro moi duoi thoi Sarri\" title=\"Kante \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/kante.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Kante v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, anh c\u00f3 1 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n v\u00e0 3 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u sao Leicester l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, anh c\u00f2n c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018&nbsp;song n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Kante v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t sung m\u00e3n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi Arsenal c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1eadp v\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng, s\u1ee9c \u00e9p \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Kante khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n linh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 \u00e1p s\u00e1t li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n khi\u1ebfn Mustafi hay Xhaka chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u01a1n, t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t, NGolo Kante t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong vai tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Maurizio Sarri. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2646","checkdouble":"195088"},{"date":"09:44 22/08","title":"Kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, Man City gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft ra sao?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/man-city-tinh-goi-lai-aro-muric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City t\u00ednh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Aro Muric thay Claudio Bravo ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i 1 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t Ederson l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady. </h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bravo ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Claudio Bravo \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9t g\u00e2n Achilles v\u00e0 trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi s\u1ebd bay sang Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea9y HLV Pep Guardiola v\u00e0o b\u00e0i to\u00e1n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1 h\u00f3c b\u00faa. \u0110\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a Man City l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t Ederton l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City t\u00ednh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Aro Muric thay Claudio Bravo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City t\u00ednh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Aro Muric thay Claudio Bravo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/man-city-tinh-goi-lai-aro-muric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bravo ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea9y Joe Hart v\u00e0 Angus Gunn t\u1edbi Burnley v\u00e0 Southampton. N\u1ebfu gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean hi\u1ec7n tr\u1ea1ng, Man City bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f4n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Ederson.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>G\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Aro Muric</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City t\u00ednh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Aro Muric \u0111ang ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i NAC Breda. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bravo sau cu\u1ed9c x\u00e9t nghi\u1ec7m chi ti\u1ebft \u1edf Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Aro Muric\" title=\"thu mon Aro Muric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/thu-mon-Aro-Muric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Man City t\u00ednh g\u1ecdi l\u1ea1i Aro Muric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAro Muric sinh ra \u1edf Zurich, Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 nh\u01b0ng l\u1edbn l\u00ean \u1edf Montenegro. Anh gia nh\u1eadp Man City t\u1eeb Grasshoppers v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2016. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n cao t\u1edbi 1m98 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 gi\u00e0u tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft NAC Breda tr\u01b0\u1edbc De Graafschap, Muric \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Man City, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng 11 l\u1ea7n sau 12 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a y\u00ean t\u00e2m, Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u01a1n xin vi\u1ec7n binh l\u00ean ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c Premier League. Chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c CLB h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb kh\u00f3a l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n nay c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-phu-nhan-mua-cillessen-vao-thang-1-172-195029.html\">Man City ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn mua sao Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-sap-mua-duoc-gavin-bazunu-172-195006.html\">Man City chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tu\u1ed5i teen</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jason-denayer-sap-roi-man-city-172-194995.html\">B\u1ea1n c\u0169 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-john-stones-172-194898.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-ruben-neves-vao-thang-1-172-194884.html\">Man City chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ruben Neves v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2645","checkdouble":"195048"},{"date":"09:37 22/08","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/6/hlv-le-thuy-hai-du-doan-thanh-tich-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c khi to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i AS h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i AS h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-du-doan-thanh-tich-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-tai-AS-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;Bahrain ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 &ldquo;\u0103n hi\u1ebfp&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1eady. \u00cdt nhi\u1ec1u, n\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 ba \u1edf m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u1ecd y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n, k\u00e9m h\u01a1n m\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 kh\u00e1t v\u1ecdng cao nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi HLV Park Hang Seo, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng 1/8 th\u00f4i, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ri\u00eang t\u00f4i, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng 1/8 th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau xa h\u01a1n cho \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD n\u0103m nay. Qua v\u00f2ng 1/8 t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft th\u00ec U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Th\u1eadt may \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i tr\u1ed9i. Palestine kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, trong khi Syria d\u00f9 g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1edbn lao l\u00e0 \u0111i t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u00e1c em \u0111ang c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1t v\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 l\u00e0m cho con ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U23 Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8 tr\u00ean SV\u0110 Patriot Candrabhaga t\u1ea1i Bekasi.&nbsp;V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p Palestine/Syria. Tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 27/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-da-biet-ro-suc-manh-cua-bahrain-168-195030.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-da-biet-ro-suc-manh-cua-bahrain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-da-biet-ro-suc-manh-cua-bahrain-168-195030.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Bahrain</span><br>\r\nTheo chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd L\u01b0u Danh Minh th\u00ec HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i mai 23/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-toan-tay-a-khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-168-194952.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-du-doan-thanh-tich-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-tai-AS-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-toan-tay-a-khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-168-194952.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n T\u00e2y \u00c1: Khi t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1ed9t nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p to\u00e0n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1m may cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2644","checkdouble":"195049"},{"date":"10:37 22/08","title":"AC Milan gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao PSG v\u1edbi Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/ac-milan-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-rabiot-voi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0110T Olympic Bahrain ch\u1ec9 mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U21 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>Mohammed Al-Hardan &ndash; ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Bahrain</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Bahrain tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f2n kh\u00e1 tr\u1ebb, \u0111a ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U21. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i, 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00e1 bi\u1ec7t c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 18 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 Bahrain c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y b\u1edfi h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, qua \u0111\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2020 v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 Olympic Tokyo 2020.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng b\u1edfi tham v\u1ecdng n\u00e0y m\u00e0 Olympic Bahrain \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Tuy v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p coi th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi trong tay h\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Mohamed Al-Hardan, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c gia T\u00e2y \u00c1 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mohammed Al-Hardan  K\u1ebb th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mohammed Al-Hardan  K\u1ebb th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Olympic-Viet-Nam-dung-toan-Tay-A-Khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mohammed Al-Hardan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mohammed Al-Hardan sinh n\u0103m 1997. L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t Bahrain l\u00e0 Al-Muharraq t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf, Al-Hardan \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed3ng trang l\u1ee9a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m 18 tu\u1ed5i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Al-Muharraq v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bahraini King's Cup ngay m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. C\u0169ng trong n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, Al-Hardan&nbsp;tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n U19 Bahrain tham d\u1ef1 VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 di\u1ec5n ra ngay t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Mohammed Al-Hardan l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. V\u1edbi nh\u00e3n quan chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 dao c\u1ea1o, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi U19 Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap U19 Bahrain gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng A.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi Mohammed Al-Hardan v\u00e0 \u0110T U19 Bahrain t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Mohammed Al-Hardan l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t do \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2. Thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng quan tr\u1ecdng, U19 Bahrain \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Tr\u1ea7n Th\u00e0nh \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 72 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup sau gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m bu\u1ed3n nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 Mohammed Al-Hardan v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. V\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ng\u00f4i sao 21 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 c\u0169 hai n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-khi-asiad-bay-gio-moi-thuc-su-bat-dau-168-194951.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-khi-asiad-bay-gio-moi-thuc-su-bat-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-khi-asiad-bay-gio-moi-thuc-su-bat-dau-168-194951.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain: Khi ASIAD b\u00e2y gi\u1edd m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u</span><br>\r\nOlympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Song tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo b\u1edfi s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p &lsquo;b\u1ecf qu\u00ean&rsquo; Al-Hardan<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Bahrain, Mohammed Al-Hardan c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Al-Hardan l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Bahrain \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i khi \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CLB Vejle Boldklub, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i tr\u1eddi \u00c2u, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Al-Hardan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, Mohammad Al-Hardan \u0111ang d\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eeba c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u00e2ng cao h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Al-Hardan, ngay c\u1ea3 BHL CLB Vejle Boldklub c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bahrain. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Jacob Kruger cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Al-Hardan ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t nhanh t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u1eadu ta \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn v\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh trong \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y \u1edf ch\u00e0ng trai n\u00e0y ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu ta \u0111\u1ebfn 2020&quot;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam tap nhe truoc tran dau voi Nhat Ban chieu 19/8\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n chi\u1ec1u 19/8\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nhat-ban-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p &lsquo;b\u1ecf qu\u00ean&rsquo; Al-Hardan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf khi m\u00e0 Al-Hardan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Olympic Malaysia \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Bahrain l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n Al-Hardan c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i anh n\u0103m x\u01b0a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao l\u00ean t\u1edbi 1m83 c\u00f9ng ngu\u1ed3n th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o, Al-Hardan ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nguy hi\u1ec3m m\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i &lsquo;ch\u0103m s\u00f3c&rsquo; r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu b\u1ecf s\u00f3t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eaft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i ra nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n l\u00fac n\u00e0y Al-Hardan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 anh t\u1eebng vay b\u1edfi l\u1ee9a Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh n\u0103m x\u01b0a. Tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Bahrain c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Al-Hardan v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y mai 23/8. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean c\u00e1c k\u00eanh s\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a VOV v\u00e0 VTC. Ngo\u00e0i ra NHM c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng Internet th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">https://beta.vtcnow.vn/kenh/vtc3<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">https://vtc.gov.vn/kenh/vtc3<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-toan-tay-a-khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-168-194952.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-du-doan-thanh-tich-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-tai-AS-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-toan-tay-a-khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan-168-194952.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n T\u00e2y \u00c1: Khi t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1ed9t nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p to\u00e0n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1m may cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span>Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2643","checkdouble":"195051"},{"date":"10:48 22/08","title":"B\u1ecb Mourinho \u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Smalling n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/27/bi-mourinho-day-ai-tren-bang-ghe-du-bi-smalling-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chris Smalling n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay v\u00ec ra \u0111i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Smalling b\u1ecb Mourinho b\u1ecf r\u01a1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Chris Smalling l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Chris Smalling n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Chris Smalling n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Lien-tuc-ngoi-du-bi,-Chris-Smalling-noi-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng Smalling kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Anh, nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sung s\u1ee9c s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Song th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Victor Lindelof v\u00e0 Eric Bailly. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng Smalling mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Italia v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u sao Fulham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Smalling l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chris Smalling n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh thay v\u00ec ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Smalling vs Tottenham\" title=\"Smalling vs Tottenham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/23/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-18,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Smalling tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng khi t\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. HLV c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n t\u00f4i ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. T\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi M.U v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Lindelof v\u00e0 Bailly ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn thua Brighton \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Smalling s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tottenham \u1edf v\u00f2ng 3. Hi\u1ec7n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang x\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa BXH Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2642","checkdouble":"195052"},{"date":"10:32 22/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Stoke vs Wigan 02h00 ng\u00e0y 23/8 (H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/22/nhan-dinh-stoke-vs-wigan-02h00-ngay-238-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Stoke vs Wigan 02h00 ng\u00e0y 23/8 (V\u00f2ng 4 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Stoke vs Wigan 02h00 ng\u00e0y 238 H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Stoke vs Wigan 02h00 ng\u00e0y 238 H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/Stoke-vs-Wigan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Stoke vs Wigan</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span>Stoke vs Wigan: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nDo l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng t\u1eeb Premier League n\u00ean Stoke \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf Championship 2018/19. Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n sau 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. S\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ch\u01a1i \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh nh\u01b0 Choupo-Moting, Afobe, Bojan Krkic, Fletcher hay Charlie Adam nh\u01b0ng Stoke ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Leeds v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brentford, Preston b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Stoke ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0 nua n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c suy gi\u1ea3m phong \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Stoke c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ed5n khi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Wigan sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Championship t\u1eeb League One. 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 3 v\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Wigan n\u1eb1m \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi 3 v\u00f2ng v\u1eeba qua h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n ghi t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 2 b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Wigan c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch n\u00ean c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1eeda nh\u1eefng l\u1ed7i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nStoke: Butland, Bauer, Martins Indi, Shawcross, Pieters, Allen, Fletcher, Choupo-Moting, Afellay, Bojan Krkic, Crouch.<br>\r\nWigan: Jones, Byrne, Bruce, Dunkley, Burn, Jamie Walker, Nick Powell, Power, Vaughan, Cole, Grigg.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2641","checkdouble":"195053"}]}